values:
how long was i sleeping?  i went down to curl around that wide heater pipe -- the one down in the boiler room, you know?  i sleep there all the time; my room isn't nearly warm enough for me.

so anyways, i went to sleep there, and i must have been asleep for a <i>looooong</i> time .. because now there are all of these new people here!  and i am very hungry.

will somebody tell shia what is going on?  &hearts;

things have been perking up!  shia has made a new friend from the spiked-haired man -- he is <i>very</i> warm, by the way, so great to wrap around~!

so now that shia has both made a friend, -and- acquired a heat source, i am both happy and healthy!

i hope to meet more nice, friendly people on this ship.~  &hearts;
